      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6e87a6f9a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6ea03f6df.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6ea0b86a2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6ea0dc6f8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6ea0d8403.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6ea04cf7f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6ea054112.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6ea031abe.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6ea0e6348.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6ea0b44aa.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Maxed version&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;This update adds a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;maxed&lt;/span&gt; version of the mod&lt;br&gt;      with &lt;span class="PurpleColor"&gt;defence set to 20&lt;/span&gt; on each piece.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;This should allow you to use Paya's attire on&lt;br&gt;      combats getting a nice protection.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;The&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;default &lt;/span&gt;version is still available, and it&lt;br&gt;      offers&lt;span class="PurpleColor"&gt; defence 3&lt;/span&gt; on each piece.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;DESCRIPTION&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;This mod is a variation of &lt;b&gt;Paya's outfit&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;and includes the traditional short &lt;b&gt;Sheikah tunic&lt;/b&gt;, the big&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;hat&lt;/b&gt; and the &lt;b&gt;sandals&lt;/b&gt;. You can find it in three chests, placed&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;outside Impa's house&lt;/b&gt;, on Kakariko Village.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/ps_attire.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; * Please note this mod is intended for &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Linkle 2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; *&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Linkle 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;users will need the &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/441448"&gt;Unofficial Patch&lt;/a&gt; installed too.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;SETUP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;There are &lt;b&gt;two versions of the mod&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;in the downloads section.&lt;br&gt;Please download just one,&amp;nbsp;install it with BCML and select one option when asked:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The &lt;b&gt;default&lt;/b&gt; one has &lt;b&gt;defence set to 3&lt;/b&gt; on each piece.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;The &lt;b&gt;maxed &lt;/b&gt;one has &lt;b&gt;defence set to 20&lt;/b&gt; on each piece.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/664e6ea03f6df.jpg" width="60%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;OTHER MODS OF MINE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;ul type="square"&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the Stylish Linkle (makeup, earrings, glasses)&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/331562"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the newest Girly Animation Pack&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/49763"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(several options).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the Clear Camera UI&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/296638"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(used to get the screenshots).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Get the Linkle mod with a different hairstyle&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/356075"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ko-Fi:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;https://ko-fi.com/i2mods&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;You can&amp;nbsp;support my works by buying me a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;?&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;coffee&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;:)&lt;br&gt;</description>
