      <author>i2m</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/49763</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/49763#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">f889920512d96f3219318aa59278a0678123d8d2</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 May 2025 22:14:48 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/682f9df557c65.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/682f9d7d08374.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/682f9d7d3ba1c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fe12aa2906b4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fe12aa699fbc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fe914ba339ef.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/5fe12ab3298ee.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6011fc5d267ef.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/603adb96e36da.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/603adf6e9a1d6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/61a9461f0dff9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/61a9461ecbe64.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6218100147823.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/62181000eb62e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/62181000f1e9c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/62181016862bd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Version 10.8&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(255, 94, 157)"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fourth Anniversary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(110, 225, 108)"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thanks you very much for your support all this time!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(255, 78, 78)"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;Changelog:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153)"&gt;Small addition to the section 5: &lt;/span&gt;"Girly running with default dash"&lt;span style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153)"&gt;, made for all the people that has been asking for it lately. Please note there is an small odd transition from running to dash running that cannot be addressed, but it's almost unnoticeable.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_00.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_index_c.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;Info &amp;amp; Acknowledgments&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;Installing the Mod&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;Description of every option&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;Troubleshooting&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;Other Mods&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_info_c.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod brings a big overhaul over Link’s more common animations: idles, walk, run, talk… a hundred of animations have been replaced in order to give to a female player, a more girly appearance, as seen in most of the female NPC in the game.&amp;nbsp;Several styles for each replacement are available to mix and get an almost unique style for your gameplay. But in fact, now you can&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;reverse it&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;and apply&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;default Link animations&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;(so, for example, you can bring back your beloved&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;tomboy&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;Linkle in Linkle 3!).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ko-Fi:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;https://ko-fi.com/i2mods&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Support my works by buying me a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;coffee&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;:)&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;None of this would have been possible without the invaluable help of&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1681976"&gt;Amiibolad&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(one of the key authors of&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/skins/179455"&gt;Zelda's Ballad mod&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;who kindly shared his knowledge on how to use NPC animations on the player), the collaboration of&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1739516"&gt;Sockpoppet&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(who hand-picked some of the animations and tested a lot of beta versions) and many, many people who shared their feedback in the comments section, helping me to find problems and fix issues during all this time. Also, without&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/skins/163132"&gt;Linkle mod&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;I would never have learned how to mod the game, so it was the thing responsible to put everything in motion.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_install_c.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Don't use the 1-click install option!&lt;br&gt;Please do this Instead:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;If you are upgrading or reinstalling the mod, uninstall it first.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;Download the BNP in a folder&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;install it on BCML&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;During the setup, a window with options will appear:&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Ensure you check&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;one option on each section&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Suggested ones are marked with an asterisk.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Install if&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;AFTER&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;your replacement mod (Linkle, Zelda…).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/games/6386"&gt;Nintendo Switch&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;users:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Please visit the port page &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/505453"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; (thanks to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/3290467" data-id="member_3290467"&gt;Zeus-Dev&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/168244"&gt;&lt;del&gt;Zelda's Ballad&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;users:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;del&gt;Please, ensure you have installed Zelda's Ballad&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;without custom animations&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/del&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;PS: Sadly, not available anymore due a DMCA takedown by Nintendo Co. Ltd.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/168235"&gt;Linkle 2&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;mod users:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Girly Animation Pack will just work, nothing else is needed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/406768"&gt;Linkle 3&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;mod users:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;I would suggest to also install the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/441448"&gt;Unofficial Linkle 3 Patcher&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;after&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;the Girly Animation Pack, to fix&amp;nbsp;Linkle 3.0.1&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;too long arms&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;(especially noticeable after installing the Girly Animation Pack) and also to be able to install Linkle 2 armor mods in Linkle 3. For convenience, a&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Lite&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;version of this patch has been included in the Girly Animation Pack as an extra option during the installation (you can install one or another or even both, as the full one will upgrade the Lite).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;u&gt;DISCLAIMER&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;Resources from Linkle 3 mod are used with authorization. Although it's not mandatory, to keep copyright things in order if you select Linkle 3 options you should have installed too Linkle 3 mod.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Other&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;player replacements users:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Girly Animation Pack should work, unless they have custom animations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tip:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;Once installed, in BCML you can press at any time the EXPLORE button and, in that folder, you will see the choices you made during the installation (in case you want to reinstall the mod with different options, upgrade it to a new version, etc).&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Disclaimer:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;&lt;u&gt;I'm not related to any player modding team&lt;/u&gt;, my work is independent&amp;nbsp;and I try to solve bugs and improve as much as I can on my scarce free time. This is all for fun, for me, for you, for everyone!&amp;nbsp;And as long as you enjoy it, just keep playing. Thanks you so much!&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;:)&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_description_c.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;This section explains each option in the Options Window you see during the installation:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. Standing idle&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_01a.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Girly standing *&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Your hero will wait in a cute girly style, as seen in most of the female NPC in the game.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_1b.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Linkle 3 standing&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Your hero will wait as seen in the Linkle 3 mod.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap1def.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Default Link standing&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Link animation will be used.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;After a half a minute or so, &lt;u&gt;random idles will play&lt;/u&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;see Section 16&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;2. Random idles while standing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_relax_r.apng"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_sleep_r2.apng"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_shy_r.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Girly casual *&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Will use these idles instead of the default ones:&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; -&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;Cute Relax (first picture): Played during the day or the night.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; -&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;Sleepy Head (second one): Played only during the night.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; -&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;Embarrassed (third): Played only if not wearing any shirt.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Default Link actions&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Default Link random idles will be used.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;3. Walking style&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_02a.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Girly walk *&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will walk in a cute girly style, as seen in most of the female NPC in the game.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_02b.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Positive walk&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will walk in a girly, somehow in a livelier style, as seen in some female NPC.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_02c.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;onfident walk&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will walk in a girly, more confident style as seen in a certain queen in the game.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_2d.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Linkle 3 walk&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will walk in a feminine fashion as seen in Linkle 3 mod. Install along Linkle 3 running style is recommended.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap2def.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Default Link walk&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Link animation will be used.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;4. How to stop walking&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_03a_r.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Cute extra step *&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Your hero will end walking with an extra, short graceful, small step; meaning she will still move a little when you release the controller stick (that could be dangerous in some places…).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Just stop&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will stop walking as soon as you release the controller stick.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_03c_r.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Linkle 3 stop&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will stop walking as seen on Linkle 3 mod.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Default Link stop:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; Link animation will be used.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;5. Running style&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_04a.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Girly running *&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Your hero will run in a cute girly style as seen in most of the female NPC in the game, and will dash run using Linkle 3 animation. Installing it along with the&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;Slightly slower run&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;option is recommended.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Girly running with default dash&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Same as above, but will use default Link dash animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_4b.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Linkle 3 running&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will run as in Linkle 3 mod. Install along with the&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;Default run speed&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;Linkle 3 walk&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;style is recommended.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap4def.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Default Link run&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Link animation will be used. Install along with the&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;Default run&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;speed option.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Note:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_06a.apng"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap6def.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i class="SelectedElement"&gt;&lt;u&gt;Linke 3 Dash run&lt;/u&gt; (left animation) will be used with&lt;br&gt;Girly Running and Linkle 3 running. The &lt;u&gt;default dash&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;(right animation) will be used with the other two.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;6. Running speed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Slightly slower run *&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;A slightly slower speed than default, matching the&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;girly running&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;animation option on the previous section.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Default run speed&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Vanilla game run speed, matching Linkle 3 and the default Link animation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;7. Walk &amp;amp; run on shallow waters&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_07a.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Careful Girl *&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will walk and run carefully, as she doesn't want to fall. Will work better paired with&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;Girly&lt;/u&gt;/&lt;u&gt;Positive&lt;/u&gt;/&lt;u&gt;Confident&amp;nbsp;&lt;/u&gt;walk and&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;Girly running&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;animations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_07bn.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Linkle 3&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will walk and run on shallow waters as seen on Linkle 3. Will work better paired with Linkle 3 walk and run animations.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap7def.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Default Link&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Default BOTW animations will be used for walk and run on shallow waters. Will work better paired with default walk and run animations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;8. Sit and crouch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_08a.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;SIT (without sleep) and then, crouch&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Adds a cute&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;sit&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;/&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;stand&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;again&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;by&#13;
pressing the left stick, instead of crouching. Now you can sit and relax like,&#13;
you do in other games! Once seated, move the stick to get into&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;crouching&#13;
pose&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;and move it further to&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;walk&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;sprint&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;crouched&#13;
as usual.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;SIT (with sleep) and then, crouch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Exactly the same as the previous option, and&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;your player will fall&#13;
to&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;sleep&lt;/b&gt; if you sit for a while.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Default&#13;
crouch&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;No&#13;
sitting or sleeping at all. Pressing the left stick will trigger the default&#13;
crouch system as usual.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;9. Talking style&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_09a.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Girly shy talk *&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will look somehow shy by raising one hand over the chest and lowering the head, while talking to other people.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_09b.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Happy talk&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Your hero will look happy and lively while talking to other people, raising both hands while talking to other people.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_09c.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Confident talk&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will look confident, hand on a hip, while talking to other people.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap_09d.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Linkle 3 talk&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your hero will talk as seen in Linkle 3 mod.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap9def.apng"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Default Link talk&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Your hero will just talk as Link.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;10. Selfies style&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/gap10new.png"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&l